{"success":true,"data":[{"id":19,"text":"A friend like you is precious and rare,\nYour friendship shows how much you care.","language":"English","lineCount":"2","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:40:39.470Z"},{"id":15,"text":"Your smile brightens every day,\nIn your presence, I want to stay.","language":"English","lineCount":"2","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:17:42.013Z"},{"id":17,"text":"Your smile brightens every day,\nIn your presence, I want to stay.\n\nYour laughter fills the air with joy,\nMy love for you will never fade away.","language":"English","lineCount":"4","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:40:16.561Z"},{"id":5,"text":"Your smile brightens every day,\nIn your presence, I want to stay.\n\nYour laughter fills the air with joy,\nMy love for you will never fade away.","language":"English","lineCount":"4","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:10:12.635Z"},{"id":21,"text":"In every season, calm or storm,\nYour steadfast presence keeps me warm.\n\nThrough darkest nights and brightest days,\nYour love illuminates my ways.\n\nWhen shadows fall and doubts appear,\nYour whispered words dissolve all fear.\n\nAcross the years, our bond grows strong,\nA timeless love where we belong.","language":"English","lineCount":"8","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:48:34.848Z"},{"id":22,"text":"?? ?? ?? ?? ?,\n?? ?? ?? ? ??? ??? ?","language":"Hindi","lineCount":"2","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:53:00.167Z"},{"id":18,"text":"?? ?? ?? ?? ?,\n?? ?? ?? ? ??? ??? ?","language":"Hindi","lineCount":"2","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:40:27.760Z"},{"id":23,"text":"??? ? ??? ???? ?,\n?? ?? ?? ??? ??? ?\n?? ??? ?? ???? ?,\n??? ? ? ?? ?? ?","language":"Hindi","lineCount":"4","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:54:18.110Z"},{"id":20,"text":"??? ? ??? ???? ?,\n?? ?? ?? ??? ??? ?\n?? ??? ?? ???? ?,\n??? ? ? ?? ?? ?","language":"Hindi","lineCount":"4","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:48:21.536Z"},{"id":16,"text":"तेरी मुस्कान में कुछ ऐसा असर है,\nदिल मेरा बस तुझी पर बेखबर है।\nतेरे बिना ये ज़िंदगी अधूरी सी लगे,\nतू ही मेरी चाहत, तू ही मेरा सफर है।","language":"Hindi","lineCount":"4","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:24:25.251Z"},{"id":24,"text":"? ??? ?? ?? ?,\n??? ?? ??? ?\n???? ?? ? ?? ?,\n??? ??? ? ???? ?? ?\n???? ?? ? ??? ??,\n??? ? ???? ??? ?? ?\n? ?? ? ??? ??? ?,\n?? ? ??? ??? ?","language":"Hindi","lineCount":"8","recipient":"General","messageType":"General","story":"","createdAt":"2026-04-06T09:54:31.463Z"}],"total":11}
